{"tid":772860,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《God of War 4》8月尾推出二週目 (New Game+)！","createTime":"2018-08-09T05:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T06:18:03.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bbcb99f8bb066c3362ce9ba9bac2999a44f0b1","tid":772860,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/157911314231532/posts/1853692734653373/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F157911314231532%2Fposts%2F1853692734653373%2F&d=YAiwTaAOMRcLGJI5bW5Urr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=80e8c6d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/157911314231532/posts/1853692734653373/</a>"},{"pid":"47c26f8a9fc2cdc1ae309c8af7ed9fe10c69179f","tid":772860,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"【戰神．新體驗】《God of War》New Game+ 8月20日免費更新：<a href=\"https://playstn.asia/2ARojvC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplaystn.asia%2F2ARojvC&d=YAiwTaAOMRcLGJI5bW5Urr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=43973ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://playstn.asia/2ARojvC</a> &lt;內容介紹&gt;<br />\n<br />\n紀念遊戲推出四個月 &mdash;&mdash; <br />\n&bull; 帶上原有裝備，重新挑戰更高等敵人，考驗戰鬥技巧；<br />\n&bull; 收集新資源「爐渣」，透過頂尖鐵匠升級最頂級裝備； <br />\n<br />\n很期待看看哪位玩家能第一個完成「追求戰神體驗+」模式，那可是了不起的成就！"},{"pid":"0ddb856ffc3962990e9a004d1f9f5f242c7ee34f","tid":772860,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"《God of War》新遊戲+ 將於8月20日以免費更新的方式登場（當天是遊戲推出的4個月紀念）。別忘了，想要體驗精彩的新遊戲+，必須先完成《God of War》任一難易度的劇情模式。如果你已經完成劇情，8月20日更新完後，新遊戲+ 就會等著你來挑戰。如果你還沒破關，朋友，你還有兩個禮拜的時間可以努力。你的船、戰斧和孩子都還在等著你呢。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://asia.playstation.com/content/dam/pscom/hk/latest-news/2018/20180809_GOW_NewGame/42694825932_89819f2c1a_k-755x425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fpscom%2Fhk%2Flatest-news%2F2018%2F20180809_GOW_NewGame%2F42694825932_89819f2c1a_k-755x425.jpg&h=0e62d2cb&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f16ffcdc1bfcc01def0397635de1b5873f348c8b","tid":772860,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"《God of War》新遊戲+究竟是什麼？此新內容源於各位玩家的回饋。<br />\n新遊戲+有全新的裝備、更強大的敵人，還可以跳過過場動畫！<br />\n <br />\n&middot;         重新體驗克雷多斯和阿特柔斯的旅程，帶上你原有的盔甲、咒術、護身符、資源，並且自選難易度重新挑戰。<br />\n&middot;         挑戰更高等的敵人，考驗自己的技巧；有些敵人甚至還有新招式！<br />\n&middot;         新遊戲+中有專屬的新裝備稀有度可供製作、升級！收集新資源「爐渣」，透過我們的頂尖鐵匠之手，升級成最頂級的裝備。<br />\n&middot;         全新強大盔甲全套和咒術賦予你全新的自訂選擇，探索全新玩法。<br />\n&middot;         最後，破關一次後，即可在一般及新遊戲+模式中跳過過場動畫，馬上繼續遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n這是《God of War》至今規模最大的更新！我們很期待看看哪位玩家能第一個完成「ˋ追求戰神體驗+」模式，那可是了不起的成就！非常感謝各位的耐心等待，讓我們能有充裕的時間開發新遊戲+模式。8月20日，正式登場。"},{"pid":"8c629839c3f6df6f963ce06d24b03dd620d88759","tid":772860,"uid":140852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"We need god of war 5 !!!"},{"pid":"4e5a7c95e383b36a9435ab8a5c553ed02ac397c8","tid":772860,"uid":20539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"白金完放左驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab99703491f2949baeb73fb72f2988b473cc2ec","tid":772860,"uid":133533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T06:18:03.000Z","msg":"終於等到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}